#19500
Base of a Stairwell~
   A feint glimmer of light emanates from an old torch at the base of this
stairwell, illuminating the room well enough to navigate. The stone steps
lead up to the battlement, where the sounds of guards marching fill the air.
The sounds of a vibrant marketplace echo through the peephole in the wooden
door to the east.
~
195 32772 0 0 0 1
D1
An ornate wooden door blocks your path.
~
wooden door~
1 0 19589
D4
You can't see all the way to the top.
~
~
0 0 19501
S
#19501
On a Landing~
   The landing at the top of the stairwell leads to the battlements surrounding
the castle. The cobblestone walkway is heavily worn from the repetitive 
marching of the elven soldiers guarding the battlement. Stone archways to the 
north and east lead to the outside, while a small stone stairwell leads to the
top of the tower.
~
