#19502
Tako-Ethreina~
   An extremely large, majestic tree stands before you.  It is the largest tree
you have ever come across in your life.  The tree has a powerful, mystical
aura about it one you cannot quite discern.  Scampering all about the tree
are all sorts of small woodland creatures, seemingly at home in its branches.
~
