#19504
A Hidden Utopia~
   Sunlight illuminates the forest as the canopy becomes less dense.  The
land here is amazingly fertile.  Lush trees and plants blossom out of the
earth sheltering all sorts of wildlife.  A mother bear and her two cubs
passed by recently as indicated by the paw prints in the dirt.  The woods
seem more serene than before, almost as if the forest is inviting you to stay.
~
