#19507
A Forgotten Trail~
   The overgrowth on the trail makes the path much more difficult to follow.
A dim light from the west brightens the earth enough to see.  A long, colorful
snake slithers through the tree roots garnishing the earth.  Termites and other
small bugs flood the area, thriving on a fallen tree that has begun to rot.
