A Forgotten Trail~
   Sunlight fails to penetrate the canopy now as the only sources of light are
the beady white eyes of nearby animals.  The path is marked only by the
gaps between the towering oak trees.  Scavengers crowd the forest in
anticipation of something, or someone, dying.
