#19509
A Forgotten Trail~
  The deeper the faded dirt trail leads into the forest, the less sunlight that
escapes through the canopy and shines on the ground.  The sound of birds 
chirping fades and is replaced by eerie shrill noises and high-pitched howls.  
The ambience of this forest grows more foreboding as the path leads farther 
into the forest.
