#19576
A Lush Forest Path~
   The forest continues to gleam as the canopy opens up even more to reveal
the flourishing underbrush.  Rabbits and other small mammals scurry through
the brush and search the bushes for nuts and berries.  Several species of birds
line the upper branches of the trees as their song fills the air.
~
