#19577
A Small Clearing~
   The forest opens up as a small stream trickles down a creek bed.
Beautiful flowering plants line the edge of the creek while several large
rocks allow the path to continue across the water.  The sound of running
water combined with the lighthearted song of the birds makes this path
through the forest seem peaceful, for now.
~
