#19578
A Bend in the Path~
   The dirt trail comes to a dead end at the base of a giant oak tree as the
path fades away.  The shrubbery is even denser in this area and covers up
all sorts of wildlife living on the ground level.  A small gap in the trees to
the west reveals a new path that is even more overgrown.
~
