#19580
An Overgrown Path~
   The path is very overgrown here, hinting that this area may not have been
used in many years.  Trees grow in an odd way here, obscuring your view
of the trail ahead.  It dawns upon you that this is most unnatural, perhaps
great magics were used.  Small woodland creatures scamper about playfully,
uncaring about the oddity of the woods.  Meanwhile a mysterious chanting
resonates throughout the forest.
~
